snippet.title: MORTALITY DECOMP. KILLERS - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
When a parasite reawakens detective Clive from death, he is recruited into a secret taskforce to stop those that killed him from weaponizing this newfound immortality

Find out more at the Cuppakill site, or wishlist the game on Steam!
